  "3318730": {
    "name": "异常侦探：少女的安眠",
    "steam_appid": 3318730,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318730/extras/c5d889ac22d6c959093c87730dc876e4.avif?t=1739628355\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《异常侦探》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>带有章节式剧情和异常元素的中式步行模拟游戏</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一名初出茅庐的灵异侦探，在接受了一份不寻常的委托后，你的命运发生了转变……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将在深夜的走廊、无限循环的住宅、狭窄的小巷这三个大场景中，努力探索秘密和寻找逃离的方法。注意，这其中发生了很多异常的事情， 仿佛有什么奇怪的力量要吞噬你…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加油，少女能否得到安眠就看你的了……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>注意：本游戏略微带些紧张氛围和跳脸元素，整体剧情并不恐怖。</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >类八番出口游戏，请发现每次场景循环里的异常事物！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请留意场景里的每一个细节，这些异常事物隐藏在不起眼的角落里！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中共有3个章节，3个独立的中式场景，80多个异常，其中一些非常隐秘，等待你的挑战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由探索的场景，拥有比普通异常游戏更为丰富的可交互内容！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多结局等你探索，当你发现全部异常后将会解开隐藏最深的秘密……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>注意：本游戏部分内容靠音效推动，建议佩戴耳机以获得最佳体验。</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法展示：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318730/extras/c1eb0b2e46645082587d58c96daea9d3.poster.avif?t=1739628355\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318730/extras/c1eb0b2e46645082587d58c96daea9d3.webm?t=1739628355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318730/extras/c1eb0b2e46645082587d58c96daea9d3.mp4?t=1739628355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索场景</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318730/extras/25a111081f39d4554f5e9a778b256e9c.poster.avif?t=1739628355\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318730/extras/25a111081f39d4554f5e9a778b256e9c.webm?t=1739628355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318730/extras/25a111081f39d4554f5e9a778b256e9c.mp4?t=1739628355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现异常</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318730/extras/4bc577266f6d5634ab69139e2c14a0ad.poster.avif?t=1739628355\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318730/extras/4bc577266f6d5634ab69139e2c14a0ad.webm?t=1739628355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318730/extras/4bc577266f6d5634ab69139e2c14a0ad.mp4?t=1739628355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >灵异危机！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><a href=\"mailto:官方联系渠道：mxstudio001@163.com\">官方联系渠道：mxstudio001@163.com</a></p>",
